FBIS4-32860 "drlat104_m_94001" FBIS-LAT-94-104 Daily Report 27 May 1994 Brazil Franco Invites Aristides for Official Visit Franco Invites Aristides for Official Visit PY2805012094 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network in Portuguese 2200 GMT 27 May 94 PY2805012094 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network Portuguese BFN [Report by Claudia Moreira in Brasilia] [Text] President Itamar Franco invited Haitian President-in-exile Jean Bertrand Aristides for an official visit to Brazil during the OAS General Assembly. The idea is to hold parallel meetings to be attended by foreign ministers in the American continent, who will discuss the situation in Haiti after the coup d'etat.
